answers.answer: They say that's a sign of preeclampsia you need to go see your doc right away

My baby loves to put her foot on my right ribs and it hurts. Sometimes my bra bothers me too. I nerve thought it could be a sign of preeclampsia; I guess now I have to ask too! My BP is usually low too, so I never thought of it, but it did go up 10 pts

Ive had horrible upper right Sid. Pain, after almost 6wks of testing its been determined that it's just my gallbladder being squished by baby. Didn't have it with my daughter. Call your dr and grt checked but don't freak out like I did, thinking it was preeclampsia
